<doc id="1321731" wikidata="Q20999924" url="?curid=1321731" title="Marine Police">
<text>Marine Police may refer to:

* Water police
* Cyprus Port and Marine Police
* Gujarat Marine Police 
* Marine Police (Hong Kong)
* Marine Police Force (aka Thames River Police)
* Vietnam Coast Guard 
* Virginia Marine Police

==See also==
* Royal Marines Police</text><links>
